snippet.title: Um No Thanks Investigates
snippet.description: Real news on public issues. Real time Investigations. Willing to be and set examples for people by being an example. Civil rights activist , independent journalism , single father of 2 ,pro wrestler, comedian, and blessed for all of you in my life thanks for watching and subscribing and coming along on this journey with me. umnothanksnews@gmail.com
